Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
The most important thing for us is the technology

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:42.000
We’ve been active for over 20 years, and since 5 
 years we manufacture, sell and maintain self-service car washes

00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:46.500
It’s our main area of activity, but not the only one

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Our company is quite unusual, our managers are young people, focused 
 on progress but at the same time also experienced specialists

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Everyone are committed to our company’s growth

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:08.000
We do a lot of thing on our own – we write 
 our own software, our design office is entirely in-house structure --

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:16.500
-- this approach guarantees that our products and services are exactly 
 as we intended and we take full responsibility for them

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:24.000
We have begun producing carwashes at the favourable time – we 
 quickly became the leader of Polish car wash market

00:01:25.500 --> 00:01:31.500
Now we manufacture the largest amount of car washes in 
 the country – approx. 70 devices a year

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:39.000
Our car washes have been sold in Czech, 
 Slovakia, Bielarus, Russia, Greece and in Germany

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:43.000
At BKF we always think about our Client

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:48.500
All the technologies we implement are designed in order to 
 lower the costs and maximize the profit --

00:01:48.500 --> 00:01:52.000
-- owing to that we provide an excellent product  that is constantly improved

00:01:52.500 --> 00:01:59.000
As every modern company we take care to introduce innovative solutions, 
 one of them is our own CRM system --

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:07.500
-- amazingly fast, convenient and secure. It covers the whole lifespan of 
 the product – from order, through manufacturing up to servicing

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:12.500
Sturdiest components, perfect organization and understating of our Clients --

00:02:12.500 --> 00:02:17.000
 – this is what unique BKF products comprise of

